{
  "texts": [
    "Mathematical functions have no intentions.",
    "8 I therefore conclude that these LLMs do not perform speech acts, as they do not act at all.",
    "My case can be summarized in the following four-liner (to illocute is to perform a speech act): P1 To qualify as a speaker, a being has to be able to illocute.",
    "P2 To illocute, a being must have intentions.",
    "P3 LLMs have no intentions."
  ]
}